                            <span class="badge bg-success">Ready</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-dark text-white h-100 border-secondary">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title text-cyan">Atmosphere Stabilizer</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Menjaga tekanan oksigen di sekitar ruangan anti-gravitasi tetap optimal bagi paru-paru.</p>
                            <span class="badge bg-secondary">Update</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
