                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white-50">
                            Setiap sesi standar berlangsung selama 45 menit di dalam ruang utama.
